----------------------
Package dependencies 
----------------------
Python version 2.7.3

pandas
sklearn 
matplotlib
----------------------
Actions before running
----------------------

Edit the 'path' variable in line 2 run_svm.sh 

current : export path='/home/raid/vr308/workspace/Python/higgSVM/'
new     : export path='path to the folder /higgsSVM'

----------------------
Command Line Arguments
----------------------

There are 5 running modes.

1)./run_svm.sh [no args]
2)./run_svm.sh uniform_sample train
3)./run_svm.sh choice_sample train
4)./run_svm.sh uniform_sample test
5)./run_svm.sh choice_sample test

Notes :

1) would default to 5)
Running under train mode will run cross validation, persist results, plots and then conduct training. 
Running under test mode will only run results under optimized parameters.

CV results are in /Results
Plots are in /Graphs
Data is in /Data

